OL,3,CFamilies say Nottingham attack victims
OL,4,C'failed by authorities' after report
OL,6,FThe families of Nottingham attacker
OL,7,FValdo Calocane's victims have said
OL,8,Ftheir relatives were "badly failed by
OL,9,Fthe authorities" following a report by
OL,10,Fa police watchdog.
OL,12,FThe report by the Independent Office
OL,13,Fof Police Conduct (IOPC) into police
OL,14,Fhandling of Calocane ` who killed 19-
OL,15,Fyear-old students Barnaby Webber and
OL,16,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar and 65-year-old
OL,17,Fcaretaker Ian Coates in June 2023 `
OL,18,Ffound a string of errors which meant
OL,19,Fhe remained free, according to The Sun.
