OL,3,CFamilies say Nottingham attack victims
OL,4,C'failed by authorities' after report
OL,6,FIt said Leicestershire Police officers
OL,7,Ffailed to arrest Calocane and did not
OL,8,Finterview witnesses after they were
OL,9,Fcalled to reports of him punching one
OL,10,Fperson in the face and pushing over a
OL,11,Fwoman at a warehouse in Kegworth, one
OL,12,Fmonth before the attacks in Nottingham.
OL,14,FThe report, seen by the paper, also
OL,15,Ffound they failed to check the police
OL,16,Fnational computer, which would have
OL,17,Fidentified Calocane was wanted for an
OL,18,Fattack on a police officer in
OL,19,FNottinghamshire in 2022, as well as
OL,20,Fnot downloading CCTV footage of the
OL,21,Fwarehouse attack.
