OL,3,CFamilies say Nottingham attack victims
OL,4,C'failed by authorities' after report
OL,6,FThe IOPC labelled the investigation "a
OL,7,Fmissed opportunity" to prevent further
OL,8,Fattacks and "exceptionally poor", but
OL,9,Fdid not recommend gross misconduct
OL,10,Fcharges against the Leicestershire
OL,11,Fofficers for which they could be
OL,12,Fsacked. They will face a misconduct
OL,13,Fhearing.
OL,15,FIn a statement to The Sun, the
OL,16,Fvictims' families said: "The damning
OL,17,Ffailures exposed by this investigation
OL,18,Fare just another example of how our
OL,19,Floved ones were badly failed by the
OL,20,Fauthorities.
