OL,3,CFamilies say Nottingham attack victims
OL,4,C'failed by authorities' after report
OL,6,F"If the police had just done their
OL,7,Fjobs properly by performing a simple
OL,8,Fcheck on the police national computer,
OL,9,FBarnaby, Grace and Ian might still be
OL,10,Falive today."
OL,12,FThey said they felt let down by the
OL,13,FIOPC investigation, saying it was of
OL,14,F"very poor quality".
OL,16,F"The police force in question and the
OL,17,Fwatchdog supposed to hold them to
OL,18,Faccount are not fit for purpose," they
OL,19,Fsaid.
