OL,4,C'failed by authorities' after report
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister last week told the
OL,7,Ffamilies that a judge-led public
OL,8,Finquiry will take place in "a matter
OL,9,Fof weeks".
OL,11,FCalocane was sentenced to an
OL,12,Findefinite hospital order in January
OL,13,F2024 after admitting manslaughter by
OL,14,Fdiminished responsibility and
OL,15,Fattempted murder.
